=== Style Guide ===
If you want to work on Xinha code, please adhere to the [wiki:Documentation/DevelopingForXinha/StyleGuide Style Guide]

=== Event Hooks ===
There are a bunch of event hooks that can be used from within plugins or the config  that can be used to perform some action at specific events that happen in the editor.[[BR]]
[wiki:Documentation/DevelopingForXinha/EventHooks Event Hooks]

